{"tid":512660,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"溫 翠 蘋 與 外 籍 老 公 離 婚","createTime":"2017-12-28T17:08:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T10:54:27.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"be9aa60776f04296464ef278e7537f5ab2a16043","tid":512660,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T17:08:47.000Z","msg":"台灣藝人溫翠蘋今年3月喪妹，上月現身仍難掩激動，昨日台灣《蘋果》報道，指她和美籍老公Kevin三年婚姻告吹，今年9月已分居並協議離婚，預計溫翠蘋明年3月便回復單身。<br />\n<br />\n第二度離婚的溫翠蘋，回覆台灣傳媒坦承婚變，又表示未來應該不會再婚了，和女兒一起過下半輩子。溫翠蘋又指雙方是感情變淡，沒有第三者。她說：「我們雖然同住屋簷下，但各自做各自的事，缺乏心靈交流。他很善良，也謝謝他給我這段美好的回憶，彼此祝福。」問到可有打算回台復出演藝圈？溫翠蘋表示：「等我女兒高中畢業，上大學之後再決定。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171228/large/28ec1p8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171228%2Flarge%2F28ec1p8.jpg&h=2b449efc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8eb00255657d49772b0185b5c10644a1e21e2b40","tid":512660,"uid":38539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T04:01:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e018b974e2db79aaae784e9fcf81b45370264c4","tid":512660,"uid":121473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T04:17:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢個唔識"},{"pid":"0bb5c1be0bc30c3ff3f5e60c9c2b57720445b8fa","tid":512660,"uid":23907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T04:19:58.000Z","msg":"好撚肯會有人接手<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51946a9d2ccebfb8b281fd02dd08c59aa8898516","tid":512660,"uid":65435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T10:41:29.000Z","msg":"milf<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a80c8c36156be06d9e1a1974e586